<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bem-vindo ao {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .brand {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .brand-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .brand-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #111827;
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .welcome-box {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
        }
        
        .steps-container {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .step {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 12px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .step-content {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(229,231,235,0) 0%, rgba(209,213,219,1) 50%, rgba(229,231,235,0) 100%);
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .social-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 8px;
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 36px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .social-icon:hover {
            background-color: #d1d5db;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #6b7280;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            color: #3b82f6;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 25px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }
            
            h2 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .button {
                padding: 14px 28px;
            }
            
            .welcome-box {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="brand">
                <div class="brand-icon">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M12 2C6.47715 2 2 6.47715 2 12C2 17.5228 6.47715 22 12 22C17.5228 22 22 17.5228 22 12C22 6.47715 17.5228 2 12 2Z" stroke="#3B82F6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        <path d="M12 16V12M12 8H12.01" stroke="#3B82F6" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <span class="brand-name">{{appName}}</span>
            </div>
            <h1>Bem-vindo à nossa comunidade!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Olá {{username}},</h2>
            
            <p>É com grande alegria que damos as boas-vindas ao <strong>{{appName}}</strong>! Sua jornada de aprendizado está prestes a começar.</p>
            
            <div class="welcome-box">
                <p>Sua conta foi criada com sucesso e agora você tem acesso completo a todos os recursos da nossa plataforma de ensino.</p>
                
                <div class="button-container">
                    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Acessar Minha Conta</a>
                </div>
                
                <p><small>Se o botão não funcionar, copie e cole este link: <span style="word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace;">{{loginUrl}}</span></small></p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Comece sua jornada:</h3>
            
            <div class="steps-container">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <strong>Complete seu perfil</strong>
                        <p>Adicione suas informações para personalizar sua experiência de aprendizado.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <strong>Explore os cursos</strong>
                        <p>Descubra conteúdos cuidadosamente preparados para seu desenvolvimento.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <strong>Conecte-se com outros</strong>
                        <p>Interaja com colegas e instrutores para enriquecer sua experiência.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p><strong>Precisa de ajuda?</strong><br>
            Nossa equipe está sempre disponível para te ajudar. Entre em contato através do e-mail <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #3b82f6;">{{supportEmail}}</a> ou visite nossa <a href="{{helpUrl}}" style="color: #3b82f6;">Central de Ajuda</a>.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://facebook.com/profile.php?id=61565792531619" class="social-icon">f</a>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/nordinomaviedev/" class="social-icon">ig</a>
                <a href="https://github.com/Mavton23" class="social-icon">git</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nordino-mavie-developer-ab6824357/" class="social-icon">lk</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="{{helpUrl}}" class="footer-link">Ajuda</a>
                <a href="{{terms}}" class="footer-link">Termos</a>
                <a href="{{privacy}}" class="footer-link">Privacidade</a>
            </div>
            <p>Atenciosamente,<br><strong>Equipe {{appName}}</strong></p>
            <p>© {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #3b82f6; text-decoration: none;">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>